{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-32-pandigital-products","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 32: Proizvod sa svim ciframa","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kaže se da broj sa ciframa <code>n</code> je pandigitalan ako koristi sve cifre od 1 do <code>n</code> samo jednom; na primer, broj sa ciframa 5, 15234, je pandigitalan od 1 do 5.</p>\n<p>Proizvod 7254 je jedinstven, jer identifikator, 39 × 186 = 7254, koji uključuje proizvođača, distributera i proizvod, sadrži sve cifre od 1 do 9.</p>\n<p>Pronađi sve proizvode čiji identifikator proizvođača/dobavljača/proizvoda može biti napisan sa svim ciframa od 1 do <code>n</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> Neki proizvodi mogu biti dostupni na više načina, pa obavezno osigurajte da ih uključite samo jednom u svoj ukupni iznos.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f38c1000cf542c50fe9f","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301976,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-32-pandigital-products"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function pandigitalProducts(n) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\npandigitalProducts(4);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>pandigitalProducts(4)</code> Trebalo bi da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof pandigitalProducts(4) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>pandigitalProducts(4)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>12</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(pandigitalProducts(4), 12);"},{"text":"<p><code>pandigitalProducts(6)</code> treba vratiti <code>162</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(pandigitalProducts(6), 162);"},{"text":"<p><code>pandigitalProducts(7)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>0</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(pandigitalProducts(7), 0);"},{"text":"<p><code>pandigitalProducts(8)</code> bi trebalo da vrati <code>13458</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(pandigitalProducts(8), 13458);"},{"text":"<p><code>pandigitalProducts(9)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>45228</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(pandigitalProducts(9), 45228);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-32-pandigital-products","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-33-digit-cancelling-fractions","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-31-coin-sums","id":"5900f38c1000cf542c50fe9f","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-32-pandigital-products"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}